{"tid":1292353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我返工 同個patient講政治","createTime":"2019-07-07T09:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T08:43:09.000Z","uid":66390,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9cc1a096bde6e1f8789c4783c018db85ddce27ad","tid":1292353,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"Patient A 一直同隔來床屌緊老董同林鄭<br />\n係咁屌普教中 話英文先係同國際接軌 呢個政府係要令學生退步<br />\n<br />\n我覺得幾岩聽 但幾粒鐘後返去 佢一樣屌緊普教中<br />\n我就講左句「咁你覺得呢家啲年輕人咁激 岩唔岩」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Patient A<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />緊係唔岩啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣衝法唔岩囉 你坐下就得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />坐左幾耐？成個2014年都坐緊 有咩用？佢唔聽 只能夠行動升級<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉 你咪講呢啲啦 我同你講 個班後生仔比人煽動嫁！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下...煽咩動 我敢講 佢地無被煽動 點解你會講得出口 有咩證據<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔知姐 點解有咁多一齊圍個警總呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />共同意識囉 大家內心都憤怒 對準一件事 呢個就係共同意識 煽咩動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能你唔係啦 但你點知執邊個個係咪呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.... （我繼續做緊手頭上既工作） 拿...我唔同你拗啦 但我想講 我唔會因為政見唔同而唔醫你 呢個就係我同差佬既分別<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n到Patient B <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次我唔出聲啦 <br />\n有個HCA同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傾計 傾美國佬<br />\n話美國佬一定贏共產黨<br />\n<br />\n個HCA就問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你覺得....呢家啲後生仔 咁激岩唔岩<br />\n衝哂入立法會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />緊係唔好啦 班後生仔前途點算呀？你諗下...咁辛苦讀產大學 就咁就無左....（之後一直探討前途問題）<br />\n<br />\n個HCA話： 岩啦！ 我發現我同你有計傾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我其實無特別喜悅 <br />\n但我好感動 有少少想喊<br />\n因為我發現呢位老人家<br />\n一句都無譴責年青人<br />\n反而只係擔心佢既前途 <br />\n<br />\n我感覺到呢位老人家 雖然唔認同 但佢無割蓆 無指責 只係出於一份擔心 一傷擔心大於一切<br />\n<br />\n我覺得咁多間大學既校長 應該係咁<br />\n當全世界都譴責緊年青示威者時<br />\n身為大學校長 唔係更應該保護學生？<br />\n而唔係爭崩頭作出譴責！<br />\n譴撚完 又如何？<br />\n只會令學生仇恨憎加 對呢間學校愈來愈失望<br />\n甚至步向絕望"},{"pid":"23a928e4419a394603ecfb0aa8e10476007b4dcd","tid":1292353,"uid":66390,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"校長 我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"078d8e407e2416115b1e41d99407fb934665b8d1","tid":1292353,"uid":66390,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AJWGgZe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAJWGgZe.png&h=889b981d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a39f92ee75afb3e18427332953fed182fbbac1df","tid":1292353,"uid":190727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:28:59.000Z","msg":"阻你少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20UgQgK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20UgQgK.png&h=a2f6a0f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6805b323952489750a70c78e53b12bd59d099a0e","tid":1292353,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"支翔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53346f517d655cca016156b1ab078e7d36ac87a4","tid":1292353,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a39f92ee75afb3e18427332953fed182fbbac1df","tid":1292353,"uid":190727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:28:59.000Z","msg":"阻你少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20UgQgK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20UgQgK.png&h=a2f6a0f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:30:16.000Z","msg":"岩岩收工 來緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來緊既時候 打呢篇野特別有feel"},{"pid":"ad1e1da0643d11eb3387f666585c83167c1e3ed3","tid":1292353,"uid":66390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6805b323952489750a70c78e53b12bd59d099a0e","tid":1292353,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"支翔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:31:10.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母！相比之下 好撚掛住個鬼佬<br />\n雖然佢都係半舊屎"},{"pid":"f98a3ef54b8c085a02191e403eab14cb4809e7e7","tid":1292353,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:31:23.000Z","msg":"支那翔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98461493f8071c4a053fa64f81000dc3c6c97f35","tid":1292353,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"推介佢上連登睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多時冇上連登的人都唔知我地諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17eef083f8cafe2d9ce2ecc0edbcf62661df9a5","tid":1292353,"uid":258217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:32:15.000Z","msg":"感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返唔到香港，真心唔知真實情況係點，已經比太多負面資訊影響到，有時聽下好人好事會知道其實香港仲有一班心水清既前輩，老人家"},{"pid":"9da24349f3caad8204ea9fb816650b894b9a1e85","tid":1292353,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98461493f8071c4a053fa64f81000dc3c6c97f35","tid":1292353,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"推介佢上連登睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多時冇上連登的人都唔知我地諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"但就係呢份出自內心既真誠長輩味道<br />\n感動到我呢個年輕人"},{"pid":"3f83b83f9e1f9a9657ba7adbe277a7ebd2b09a54","tid":1292353,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:36:02.000Z","msg":"呢個老人家....<br />\n以僅有既活動能力 震住咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲撚想喊"},{"pid":"a30848229404d2fb5203f09a1d60ad9eb693a819","tid":1292353,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086058e4880617d31bdbdda3d5bc0247c5466d86","tid":1292353,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad1e1da0643d11eb3387f666585c83167c1e3ed3","tid":1292353,"uid":66390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6805b323952489750a70c78e53b12bd59d099a0e","tid":1292353,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"支翔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:31:10.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母！相比之下 好撚掛住個鬼佬<br />\n雖然佢都係半舊屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"鬼佬坐唔穩啊, 比人攪後面(校委會)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbcabee490a63b95e6bc8d0ebfece03730921d3","tid":1292353,"uid":5739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:43:39.000Z","msg":"已經轉晒台做99<br />\n諗住同啲支那patient宣傳"},{"pid":"bcf93dd8753d5fd022ec27402a60de057f4d3eb5","tid":1292353,"uid":161222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"078d8e407e2416115b1e41d99407fb934665b8d1